<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Welcome to CLEAR Learning | Getting Started</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600;700&family=Source+Sans+3:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="https://assets-002.noviams.com/novi-file-uploads/clear/structure/clearlogo.png">
<style>
  :root {
    --burgundy: #64092C;
    --burgundy-dark: #4a0620;
    --burgundy-light: #8a1040;
    --gold: #DDA838;
    --gold-light: #f0c45e;
    --charcoal: #484848;
    --blue: #084D78;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --off-white: #faf8f5;
    --light-gray: #f2f0ed;
    --border: #e0dbd4;
    --text-muted: #7a6e68;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
    background: var(--off-white);
    color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* HEADER */
  .page-header {
    background: var(--burgundy);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 48px 40px 40px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .page-header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -60px; right: -60px;
    width: 300px; height: 300px;
    background: var(--burgundy-light);
    border-radius: 50%;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }
  .page-header::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -80px; left: 40%;
    width: 200px; height: 200px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    opacity: 0.12;
  }
  .header-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .header-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Source Sans 3', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 2.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .header-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 38px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .header-subtitle {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    font-weight: 300;
    max-width: 560px;
  }
  .gold-rule {
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), transparent);
    margin: 24px 0 0;
    border: none;
  }

  /* LAYOUT */
  .page-body {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 24px 80px;
  }

  /* SECTION HEADINGS */
  .section {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .section-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
  }
  .section-icon {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    background: var(--burgundy);
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .section-icon svg {
    width: 18px; height: 18px;
    fill: var(--white);
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--burgundy);
  }

  /* PROSE */
  .prose p {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }
  .prose p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* CALLOUT BOXES */
  .callout {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 16px 20px;
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    margin: 16px 0;
    font-size: 14.5px;
  }
  .callout.info {
    border-color: var(--blue);
    background: #f0f6fb;
  }
  .callout.warning {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    background: #fdf8ee;
  }
  .callout strong {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* CARD GRIDS */
  .card-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .card-grid.cols-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  .card-grid.cols-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; }

  .card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 20px;
    font-size: 14.5px;
  }
  .card-title {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--burgundy);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  .card ul {
    padding-left: 18px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
  }
  .card ul li { margin-bottom: 4px; }

  /* REQUIREMENT ITEMS */
  .req-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .req-list2 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .req-item {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 18px 16px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .req-item .req-icon {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    display: block;
  }
  .req-item .req-label {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--burgundy);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .req-item .req-detail {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  /* EXAM BOX */
  .exam-box {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-top: 4px solid var(--burgundy);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 24px;
  }
  .exam-box .exam-label {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--burgundy);
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .exam-details {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .exam-detail-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 14.5px;
  }
  .exam-detail-item .dot {
    width: 8px; height: 8px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-top: 7px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* PORTAL SECTION — trigger cards */
  .portal-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .portal-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 20px 20px 16px;
    font-size: 14.5px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: box-shadow 0.15s, border-color 0.15s, transform 0.1s;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    text-align: left;
    width: 100%;
    font-family: inherit;
  }
  .portal-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(100,9,44,0.12);
    border-color: var(--burgundy);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }
  .portal-card:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--burgundy);
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }
  .portal-card .pc-title {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--blue);
    font-size: 15px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .portal-card .pc-title::before {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .portal-card .pc-desc {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .portal-card .pc-cta {
    margin-top: auto;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--burgundy);
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
  }
  .portal-card .pc-cta::after { content: ' →'; }

  /* MODAL */
  .modal-overlay {
    display: none;
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(40, 10, 20, 0.55);
    z-index: 1000;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 24px;
  }
  .modal-overlay.open { display: flex; }
  .modal {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 14px;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 620px;
    max-height: 88vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
    box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    animation: modalIn 0.18s ease;
  }
  @keyframes modalIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px) scale(0.98); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
  }
  .modal-header {
    background: var(--burgundy);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 22px 28px 18px;
    border-radius: 14px 14px 0 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 16px;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .modal-header-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .modal-close {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    border: none;
    color: var(--white);
    width: 30px; height: 30px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 18px;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: background 0.15s;
    font-family: inherit;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .modal-close:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.28); }
  .modal-body { padding: 24px 28px 28px; }

  /* Screenshot placeholder */
  .screenshot-placeholder {
    background: var(--light-gray);
    border: 2px dashed var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 28px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 13px;
    margin: 16px 0;
  }
  .screenshot-placeholder .sp-icon { font-size: 28px; display: block; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .screenshot-placeholder .sp-label {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
    font-size: 13.5px;
  }

  /* Modal content */
  .modal-prose p {
    font-size: 14.5px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .modal-prose p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .modal-prose strong { color: var(--burgundy); }
  .modal-prose ul { padding-left: 18px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .modal-prose ul li { font-size: 14.5px; margin-bottom: 6px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .modal-prose .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .modal-prose .step-num {
    background: var(--burgundy);
    color: var(--white);
    width: 24px; height: 24px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .modal-prose .step-text { font-size: 14.5px; color: var(--charcoal); line-height: 1.6; }
  .modal-prose .note {
    background: #f0f6fb;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--blue);
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-top: 14px;
  }

  /* DISCLAIMER */
  .disclaimer-block {
    background: var(--light-gray);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .disclaimer-block + .disclaimer-block {
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  /* CONTACT */
  .contact-strip {
    background: var(--burgundy);
    color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 22px 28px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .contact-strip .cs-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .contact-strip .cs-email {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .contact-strip .cs-email:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  /* DIVIDER */
  .divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin: 36px 0;
  }

  /* SECTION LABEL for conditional */
  .conditional-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    background: #fdf8ee;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    color: #8a6000;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  /* ANCHORED NAV */
  .toc {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  .toc-title {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 13px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .toc-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .toc-links a {
    color: var(--burgundy);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border: 1px solid #d4c4cb;
    border-radius: 20px;
    transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s;
  }
  .toc-links a:hover {
    background: var(--burgundy);
    color: var(--white);
  }

li.survey,
li.quiz,
li.ILT,
li.Independent {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
}

li.survey::before,
li.quiz::before,
li.ILT::before,
li.Independent::before {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    margin-top: 3px;
    background-size: contain;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
}

li.survey::before    { background-image: url('https://clearlearning.github.io/images/survey.png'); }
li.quiz::before      { background-image: url('https://clearlearning.github.io/images/quiz.png'); }
li.ILT::before       { background-image: url('https://clearlearning.github.io/images/ILT.png'); }
li.Independent::before { background-image: url('https://clearlearning.github.io/images/Independent.png'); }

  }
  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .card-grid.cols-2, .card-grid.cols-3,
    .req-list, .exam-details, .portal-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .header-title { font-size: 28px; }
    .contact-strip { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    .page-header { padding: 32px 20px 28px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="page-header">
  <div class="header-inner">
    <div class="header-eyebrow">CLEAR Learning</div>
    <h1 class="header-title">Welcome &amp; Getting Started</h1>
    <p class="header-subtitle">Everything you need to know before your program begins — program expectations, technical requirements, and how to navigate the portal.</p>
    <hr class="gold-rule">
  </div>
</header>

<main class="page-body">

  <!-- TABLE OF CONTENTS -->
  <nav class="toc">
    <div class="toc-title">On This Page</div>
    <div class="toc-links">
      <a href="#program-support">Program Support</a>
      <a href="#disclaimers">Disclaimers</a>
      <a href="#live-sessions">Live Session Expectations</a>
      <a href="#exam">Final Exam</a>
      <a href="#requirements">System Requirements</a>
      <a href="#software">Software Components</a>
      <a href="#portal">CLEAR Learning Portal</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- PROGRAM SUPPORT -->
  <section class="section" id="program-support">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1 17h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2V7h2v8z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Program Support</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-strip">
      <div>
        <div class="cs-label">Questions? Reach the CLEAR Learning team at</div>
        <a class="cs-email" href="mailto:clearlearning@clearhq.org">clearlearning@clearhq.org</a>
      </div>
      <div style="font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);text-align:right;line-height:1.5;">We're here to help before,<br>during, and after your program.</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- DISCLAIMERS -->
  <section class="section" id="disclaimers">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V5l-9-4zm-1 6h2v2h-2V7zm0 4h2v6h-2v-6z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Disclaimers</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="disclaimer-block" style="margin-bottom:12px;">
      <strong style="color:var(--burgundy);margin-bottom:6px;display:block;">Program Content</strong>
      The concepts taught in this program are what CLEAR deems as best practice. However, agency policies and procedures supersede the concepts taught in this program.
    </div>
    <div class="disclaimer-block">
      <strong style="color:var(--burgundy);margin-bottom:6px;display:block;">Perspectives &amp; Debate</strong>
      CLEAR is a place for novel, thoughtful, non-partisan debate, undertaken inclusively and respectfully. Those who contribute to the debate speak in their own capacity and do not necessarily represent the view(s) of CLEAR. CLEAR provides a space in which contentious issues can be safely and respectfully discussed, grounded in a sound body of professional regulatory knowledge. Acting in the public interest, regulations, and the views of regulators and the wider public, evolve over time. Discussions at CLEAR reflect this evolution of thinking, encompassing a wide variety of considered opinion.
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- LIVE SESSION EXPECTATIONS -->
  <section class="section" id="live-sessions">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17 10.5V7c0-.55-.45-1-1-1H4c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1v10c0 .55.45 1 1 1h12c.55 0 1-.45 1-1v-3.5l4 4v-11l-4 4z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Live Session Expectations</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="conditional-badge">
      <span>📋</span> Applies to programs with instructor-led live sessions
    </div>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>If your program includes live, instructor-led sessions, the following expectations apply. Not all programs include a live component — refer to your course schedule for details.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card-grid cols-3" style="margin-top:18px;">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">🎙️ Audio &amp; Participation</div>
        <ul>
          <li>All participant lines are muted during training by default</li>
          <li>To speak, click the <strong>Raise Hand</strong> icon and wait to be called on, then unmute</li>
          <li>Direct all questions in the chat to the facilitator</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">📷 Camera Policy</div>
        <ul>
          <li>Camera expectations vary by program</li>
          <li>Some programs encourage cameras on to support engagement</li>
          <li>Others keep cameras off due to cohort size or bandwidth</li>
          <li>Your facilitator will communicate the expectation for your program</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-title">☕ Breaks &amp; Activities</div>
        <ul>
          <li>Breaks occur approximately every 45–50 minutes</li>
          <li>Leave the training session open on your computer during breaks</li>
          <li>Sessions include polls, videos, and small group activities</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- FINAL EXAM -->
  <section class="section" id="exam">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Final Exam</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="conditional-badge">
      <span>📋</span> Applies only to programs that include a final exam
    </div>
    <div class="exam-box">
      <div class="exam-label">Exam-Track Programs Only</div>
      <div class="prose">
        <p>If your program culminates in a final exam, it is administered online within the CLEAR Learning Portal and proctored in real time by our testing partner, <strong>Integrity Advocate</strong>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="exam-details">
        <div class="exam-detail-item">
          <span class="dot"></span>
          <span>All exam questions are <strong>multiple choice</strong></span>
        </div>
        <div class="exam-detail-item">
          <span class="dot"></span>
          <span>Exams have a <strong>set time limit</strong> — plan accordingly</span>
        </div>
        <div class="exam-detail-item">
          <span class="dot"></span>
          <span>Three separate exam forms are used across the program</span>
        </div>
        <div class="exam-detail-item">
          <span class="dot"></span>
          <span>Proctoring is conducted live and remotely by Integrity Advocate</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="callout warning" style="margin-top:20px;">
        <strong>Program Review Session</strong>
        A Program Review Session is available prior to the exam — we strongly encourage you to attend. This session covers key concepts that will appear on the exam and provides instructions for accessing and completing it. <strong>Access to the final exam is granted only after the Review Session is complete.</strong>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <!-- SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS -->
  <section class="section" id="requirements">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-icon">
